## 📚 Literature Review

Various studies show that continuous exposure to high noise levels causes stress, health problems, and reduced productivity. Traditional sound meters lack automation, while modern IoT-based systems are costly and complex.

This project focuses on a **simple, low-cost, and real-time monitoring solution**, specifically designed for schools and hospitals. Unlike other systems, it provides immediate alerts and is easy to deploy.

